node.text: She’s here!!! My dream Lamborghini Murcielago 40th Anniversary has arrived to Utah from Toronto, Canada. I wanna thank the previous owner Angelo, @autotempest for helping me find it, @mr360cs for helping me broker the deal and of course @zachbrehl and @toronto_exotic_car_spotting for storing the car for me for 2 months as we arranged importation into the USA.
